OL,3,CBlue plaque unveiled at former home of
OL,4,Cworld champion speedway rider Ivan
OL,5,CMauger
OL,7,FA blue plaque has been unveiled at the
OL,8,Fformer Stockport home of 15-time world
OL,9,Fchampion speedway rider Ivan Mauger
OL,10,FMBE OBE.
OL,12,FWidely regarded as the best speedway
OL,13,Frider the world has ever seen, he was
OL,14,Fthe first to win a record six
OL,15,Findividual world championships, and
OL,16,Fthe first to win the individual
OL,17,Fspeedway and long track world
OL,18,Fchampionships in the same year.
