OL,3,CBlue plaque unveiled at former home of
OL,4,Cworld champion speedway rider Ivan
OL,5,CMauger
OL,7,FBorn in New Zealand, Ivan developed
OL,8,Fhis speedway career in the UK, joining
OL,9,FNewcastle in 1963 before moving to
OL,10,FBelle Vue Aces in Manchester in 1969.
OL,12,FHe won 15 titles between 1968 and 1979
OL,13,F- all but two of which while he was
OL,14,Fliving in Stockport.
OL,16,FIvan retired in 1985 following which
OL,17,Fhe and his family moved to Australia.
OL,18,FSadly, in his later years Ivan
OL,19,Fsuffered from Alzheimer's and died in
OL,20,F2018.
