OL,3,CBlue plaque unveiled at former home of
OL,4,Cworld champion speedway rider Ivan
OL,5,CMauger
OL,7,FNow the late sportsman has been
OL,8,Fhonoured with a blue plaque at his one-
OL,9,Ftime home on Chester Road, Woodford,
OL,10,FStockport, after a long campaign by
OL,11,Fspeedway fan Brian Connolly.
OL,13,FFamous figures from the speedway
OL,14,Fworld, including 1976 World Champion
OL,15,FPeter Collins, and his brother Les,
OL,16,Fwere at a ceremony for the unveiling
OL,17,Fon Thursday 11 June 2024.
OL,19,FThe plaque was unveiled by Ivan's
OL,20,Fgranddaughter Skye Raye, who travelled
OL,21,Ffrom Australia for the event.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
