OL,3,CBlue plaque unveiled at former home of
OL,4,Cworld champion speedway rider Ivan
OL,5,CMauger
OL,7,FIvan's daughter Debbie also had 100
OL,8,Flimited edition commemorative coins
OL,9,Fmade for everyone who went to the
OL,10,Fceremony.
OL,12,FIn a post on social media, Debbie said
OL,13,Fthe whole family was "overjoyed", and
OL,14,Fthanked Brian for his hard work in
OL,15,Fachieving the honour for her dad.
OL,17,FStockport Councillor Coun David
OL,18,FMeller, who approved the blue plaque,
OL,19,Fsaid: "From my perspective he is a
OL,20,Fvery worthy recipient.
