OL,7,F"What the plaque will do is raise
OL,8,Fawareness of the fantastic things he
OL,9,Fachieved during his career.
OL,11,F"In terms of sporting greats he is
OL,12,Fwell up there with Fred Perry, with
OL,13,Fhim being so dominant in his sport.
OL,14,FIt's fantastic that, as a borough, we
OL,15,Fare recognising him."
